ont-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">另一边，谷歌并没有坐以待毙，下一代Gemini旗舰模型即将出世。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">坊间传闻，Gemini 3.0最晚下周上线。今天，谷歌内部研究人员在X上，频频发文暗示——BIG THINGS！</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;margin-right:8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505148192\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5843270868824532\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1174\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1174\" data-height=\"686\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"328\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=90fd1924&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb1tjmPLTuPI39ZBXNAH8NeTUM1m8tsia3x9hVwHg08vE97K03m8M9Idx3LRBg42dZzmapFVwS4IA4Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;